            <abstract>
                <p>This record refers to a collection of prayers and miracles of the Trinity attested in 
                    <ref type="mss" corresp="ANLcr62"/> arranged according to the days of the week. While
                    its structure, introduction and miracles are identical to <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2296Sayfas"/>, the content
                    of the prayers is different and instead largely corresponds to <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4691Prayer"/>.</p>
            </abstract>
